      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "If you shall at all turn from following me ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Hebrew, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "If in turning you turn from me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "that is, if you ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "assuredly, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "indeed, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "or, as some understand it, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "altogether turn from me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "if you forsake my service, desert my altar, and go and serve other gods; (for that was the covenant-breaking sin;) if you or your children break off from me, and knowingly and wilfully violate my laws, this house will not save you. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Then will I cut off Israel — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "By one judgment after another, till they become the most despicable people under the sun, though they be now the most honourable. This implies the destruction of the royal family, though it is not particularly threatened; for the king is of course undone if his kingdom be destroyed. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And this house",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " —",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": " will I cast out of my sight — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I will not regard it, but will take away my presence and protection from it: it shall be abandoned and laid desolate. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And Israel shall be a proverb — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Their calamities and miseries shall be mentioned proverbially, to express extreme affliction and distress. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And a byword among all people — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Who would mock at their calamitous and deplorable state. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
