        "text": ". -  פּני מעל שׁלּח, to dismiss, i.e., to reject from before my face. \"This house will be עליון,\" i.e., will stand high, or through its rejection will be a lofty example for all that pass by. The temple stood upon a high mountain, so that its ruins could not fail to attract the attention of all who went past. The expression עליון is selected with an implied allusion to ",
